<!-- ════════════════ 11 · SECURITY & GOVERNANCE ════════════════ -->
  <section data-label="Security & governance" class="slide light track-security">
    <div class="glow soft"></div>
    <div class="frame">
      <p class="eyebrow"><span class="num">10</span>Voor een bank · Security &amp; governance</p>
      <h2 class="h2">AI-capaciteit moet werken <span class="accent">binnen KBC-kaders</span>.</h2>

      <div class="frame-body">
        <div class="sec-grid" style="align-content: start;">
          <div class="sec-card">
            <div class="icon-title">
              <span class="sec-ic">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <h4>Data binnen je perimeter</h4>
            </div>
            <p>Private of EU-gehoste modellen, geen training op je code of klantdata, en heldere data-residency-afspraken.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sec-card">
            <div class="icon-title">
              <span class="sec-ic">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
              </span>
              <h4>Regelgevingsbewust</h4>
            </div>
            <p>Werkwijze afgestemd op het kader waarin KBC opereert: DORA, GDPR, NIS2 en de EU AI Act, pragmatisch toegepast.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sec-card">
            <div class="icon-title">
              <span class="sec-ic">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v6m0 6v6m11-7h-6m-6 0H1"/></svg>
              </span>
              <h4>Human-in-the-loop</h4>
            </div>
            <p>Agents stellen voor, mensen beslissen. Kritieke acties altijd met expliciete goedkeuring en duidelijke grenzen.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sec-card">
            <div class="icon-title">
              <span class="sec-ic">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M9 15l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              </span>
              <h4>Auditeerbaar &amp; traceerbaar</h4>
            </div>
            <p>Logging van prompts, acties en bronnen. Volledige nazichtbaarheid voor audit, risk en compliance.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sec-card">
            <div class="icon-title">
              <span class="sec-ic">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
              </span>
              <h4>Secure SDLC</h4>
            </div>
            <p>RBAC, secret-scanning, SAST/DAST en sandboxing geïntegreerd in de pipeline. AI versnelt, beveiliging blijft.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sec-card">
            <div class="icon-title">
              <span class="sec-ic">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
              </span>
              <h4>Model- &amp; toolgovernance</h4>
            </div>
            <p>Goedgekeurde modellen en tools, versiebeheer, evaluatie en monitoring: beheersbaar i.p.v. wildgroei.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
